  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Out-Patient Appointment Consultant - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
An 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_out-patient_appointment_consultant">Out-Patient Appointment Consultant</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_appointment">APPOINTMENT</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
An 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_out-patient_appointment_consultant">Out-Patient Appointment Consultant</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_out-patient_appointment">Out-Patient Appointment</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
An 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_out-patient_appointment_consultant">Out-Patient Appointment Consultant</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_appointment">APPOINTMENT</xref>
 for a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 to see or have contact with a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_consultant">CONSULTANT</xref>
, or member of the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_consultant">CONSULTANT</xref>
 Firm, at a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_consultant_clinic">Consultant Clinic</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_appointment">APPOINTMENT</xref>
 may result in a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_clinic_attendance_consultant">Clinic Attendance Consultant</xref>
 as part of a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_consultant_out-patient_episode">Consultant Out-Patient Episode</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
Information recorded for an 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_out-patient_appointment_consultant">Out-Patient Appointment Consultant</xref>
 includes:  </p>
  <div>
      <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_attended_or_did_not_attend">ATTENDED OR DID NOT ATTEND</xref>
  </div>

